FAQ

WHAT ARE PIXIZ?

PIXIZ is a collection of algorithmically generated characters designed by the 'God of Pixiz' and minted as NFTs on the Ethereum blockchain. The 1st generation of 10,000 pixiz will be born from various attributes and colors.
